data.description: Looking for that Great 3/2 Home Located in the Desired Subdivision of The Meadows in Homosassa. Here It Is! This home features a split floor plan, updated kitchen and bathrooms.  This 3/2 Home features new Luxury Vinyl floors in Living Room, Dining Room and Kitchen along with Master Bedroom and bath. This is a great family home or forever home. Large backyard, 2 Car garage, and driveway for plenty of parking. A/C is only 2-3 years old and new water heater. Minute away to all of the major stores and restaurants on HWY 19...  Short ride to Homosassa Springs for all your boating and kayaking needs!!!
